# scripts/ Directory

## Purpose
Playwright automation scripts and helper utilities.

## Structure (V1)
```
scripts/
├── playwright/
│   ├── smoke.js        # Basic page load + error check
│   ├── screenshot.js  # Full-page screenshot export
│   ├── pdf.js         # PDF export
│   └── verify.js      # Configurable verification
├── package.json       # Minimal deps (playwright)
└── setup.sh          # (Phase 1) Install + browser download
```

## Notes
- All scripts accept CLI flags or JSON config
- Output goes to `../state/` directory
- Return exit code 0 = pass, non-zero = fail
